        "jp_clean": "(王はすすり泣いている。)",
        "checked": true
    },
    {
        "en_raw": "<span class=\"shake\">\n I suppose your story might be similar to mine, bright one......\n</span>",
        "en_clean": "I suppose your story might be similar to mine, bright one......",
        "jp_raw": "<span class=\"shake\">おまえも私と似たような境遇なのだろうな、明るき者よ......</span>",
        "jp_clean": "おまえも私と似たような境遇なのだろうな、明るき者よ......",
        "checked": true
    },
    {
        "en_raw": "<span class=\"shake\">\n One day......\n <br/>\n I just woke up on a beach, on a coast north of Vaugarde.\n</span>",
        "en_clean": "One day......I just woke up on a beach, on a coast north of Vaugarde.",
        "jp_raw": "<span class=\"shake\">ある日......<br>私は目覚めると、ヴォーガルド北部の海岸にいた。</span>",
        "jp_clean": "ある日......私は目覚めると、ヴォーガルド北部の海岸にいた。",
        "checked": true
    },
    {
        "en_raw": "<span class=\"shake\">\n I woke up slowly, as people sometimes do, expecting to remember where I was, what I was supposed to be doing that day......\n</span>",
        "en_clean": "I woke up slowly, as people sometimes do, expecting to remember where I was, what I was supposed to be doing that day......",
        "jp_raw": "<span class=\"shake\">人が時としてそうなるように、私はゆっくりと目を覚まし、自分がどこにいたのか、何をする予定だったのかを思い出そうとした......</span>",
